Features:
  Calendar
  Add events to calendar based on time or just day you would like to do them
  Shuffle event order on different days by dragging events
  Have events that are not day specific
  Have a schedule viewer to see to dos for today / anything marked as "needs doing" / missed to dos
  In this daily tasks view also include things that you would LIKE to do each day, if possible
  Dismiss functionality, especially if implementing push notifications
  Push notifications for to dos
